UserStory:
I wanna analyze what people think about covid.
I wanna use tweepy to get all users' contents and use NLP to classify the content and find out what most people are talking about.
Meanwhile, I wanna use NLP to analyze their syntax and find out how most people feel.
My model are for those who want to know the current trend.

Work currently down:
1. import Tweepy and test the function of grasping data from recently uploaded contents
2. import NLP and write four functions to analyze their sentiments and emotions, topics they talk.


 1. To connect with google cloud: Need to set up a service account and the key
 Reference: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iqRgOdJZtiY
 wibsite: https://console.cloud.google.com/iam-admin/serviceaccounts/details/111273889594197677930;edit=true?project=jianxiao602nlp&supportedpurview=project

 2. I recommend to build an virtual environment (not use iPython on google)
    reference:https://cloud.google.com/python/docs/setup

 3. to echo environment path on venv:https://www.roelpeters.be/set-environment-variables-in-virtual-environment-python/
    import os
    path="/Users/jianxiaoyang/Downloads/jianxiao602nlp-d001e4497302.json"
    path2="/Users/jianxiaoyang/Documents/EC601 software/google nlp api/jianxiao602nlp-d001e4497302.json"
    os.environ['GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS'] = path2


